graph TB
    subgraph "Model Registry Operator"
        Controller[Controller Manager]
        Webhook[Webhook Service<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS]
        Controller -->|validates CRs| Webhook
    end

    subgraph "Model Registry Instance"
        RestAPI[REST API Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP]
        RBACProxy[kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS]
        RBACProxy -->|proxies to| RestAPI

        subgraph "Optional Components"
            Postgres[PostgreSQL DB<br/>5432/TCP]
            MySQL[MySQL DB<br/>3306/TCP]
            Catalog[Model Catalog<br/>optional]
        end
    end

    User[User/Client] -->|creates| ModelRegistryCR[ModelRegistry CR<br/>v1beta1]
    ModelRegistryCR -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|creates| RestAPI
    Controller -->|creates| RBACProxy
    Controller -->|creates| Postgres
    Controller -->|creates| Service[Kubernetes Service]
    Controller -->|creates| Route[OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    Controller -->|creates| NetworkPolicy[NetworkPolicy<br/>DB isolation]

    RestAPI -->|stores metadata| Postgres
    RestAPI -.->|alternative| MySQL

    RBACProxy -->|validates authz| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>SubjectAccessReview]

    Controller -->|depends on| CertManager[cert-manager]
    Controller -->|integrates| ServiceCA[OpenShift Service CA]
    Route -.->|optional| IstioGW[Istio Gateway]

    Controller -->|watches| PlatformComponents[components.platform.opendatahub.io]
    Controller -->|watches| PlatformServices[services.platform.opendatahub.io]

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2
    style RestAPI fill:#7ed321
    style RBACProxy fill:#7ed321
    style ModelRegistryCR fill:#f5a623
    style Postgres fill:#e8e8e8
    style MySQL fill:#e8e8e8
    style CertManager fill:#e8e8e8
    style IstioGW fill:#e8e8e8
    style Catalog fill:#d3d3d3
